name: 3rd International Conference on Sustainable Expert Systems [ICSES 2022]
content: All registered and presented articles will be published in Springer Series - Lecture Notes in Networks and Systems. Publication Time: 2 to 4 months. LNNS Series is Indexed by SCOPUS, INSPEC, WTI Frankfurt eG, zbMATH, SCImago. All books published in the series are submitted for consideration in Web of Science.
organizers: Institute of Engineering (IOE), Tribhuvan University, Nepal
